snippet.title: Microsoft Developer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official Microsoft Developer YouTube channel! We feature live events, shows, tips and tutorials, product news, and more – all hosted by technical experts here at Microsoft to help you create and grow on Microsoft Azure.

Subscribe to our channel for all the latest Microsoft Developer videos!
Follow us at @LearnTV: https://twitter.com/LearnTV
